name: Sleepy Owl glass cabochon french wire earrings
description:
These pretty and dainty earrings are so cute and just perfect to compliment your favourite outfit.

The glass cabochons measure 12mm and are set on antique bronze french ear wires.
With these earring you never need to worry about finding the back and because they are drops they look perfect for a dressier look.
Please check my other listings for more designs.

Visit our facebook page at
www.facebook.com/sweetsherbet01

name: Sweet Vintage Boy with ball wooden brooch.
description:
This sweet wooden brooch is just the thing to add a pop of colour or
a funky edge to your favourite outfit.
My wooden brooches are very light and will sit beautifully 
on your clothing without pulling or adding too much weight to the fabric.
This sweet vintage style little boy wooden brooch measures approximately 25x60mm.
Please check my other listings for different colours and designs in 
our exclusive wooden brooch range.
